{"id": "1316619996025061399", "channel_id": "1316597377167130676", "type": 0, "author_id": "1300493839198457929", "author_name": "guanzheu1959_53862", "author_bot": false, "content": "最后的双发钥令给小小心愿到超限诺缔拉 直接5w秒杀", "timestamp": "2024-12-12T04:17:48.669000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1316597377167130676", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "原初之影 第七關 誕臨之視 陣容推薦", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1316650006626963457", "channel_id": "1316597377167130676", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "補個調整後的陣容，助戰隨便抓，不會打他的牌。", "timestamp": "2024-12-12T06:17:03.754000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-12-12T06:29:01.527000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1316650006521970718", "filename": "465654.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 251841, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1316597377167130676/1316650006521970718/465654.JPG?ex=69cc0f9f&is=69cabe1f&hm=6199e233f96b35cff0b813a84b69eb273557f764b12096f92f89919f2d95d98d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1316597377167130676", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "原初之影 第七關 誕臨之視 陣容推薦", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1316651555394424832", "channel_id": "1316597377167130676", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "第三回合抓拉蒙或諾覺醒，開第一鑰令抓衍生複製，複製高熱區，然後再開拉蒙狂氣抓第二張衍生複製，複製高熱區。開第二鑰令純白拿高熱。\n剩下就是按照回合，打出高熱區，數量不夠就開潘狂氣。", "timestamp": "2024-12-12T06:23:13.009000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-12-12T06:31:36.314000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1316597377167130676", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "原初之影 第七關 誕臨之視 陣容推薦", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1316651668242432001", "channel_id": "1316597377167130676", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "少數情況進牌真的很差，會沒辦法實現，但幾乎都能成立。", "timestamp": "2024-12-12T06:23:39.914000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1316597377167130676", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "原初之影 第七關 誕臨之視 陣容推薦", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1316651832063299604", "channel_id": "1316597377167130676", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "前三回合需要打一些狂氣牌來湊狂氣。", "timestamp": "2024-12-12T06:24:18.972000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1316597377167130676", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "原初之影 第七關 誕臨之視 陣容推薦", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1316652756446085172", "channel_id": "1316597377167130676", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "思路主要是用第一輪牌庫就把關卡打完，後續拿到的所有牌都是高熱，因此只需要第三回合開一次純白。", "timestamp": "2024-12-12T06:27:59.362000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1316597377167130676", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "原初之影 第七關 誕臨之視 陣容推薦", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1316652823097770045", "channel_id": "1316597377167130676", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "也只有第三回合之前需要操作一下，後續時間都是放空打高熱。", "timestamp": "2024-12-12T06:28:15.253000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-12-12T06:28:27.220000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1316597377167130676", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "原初之影 第七關 誕臨之視 陣容推薦", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
